column6: French青豆的的菜脯材料准备 ：    法式青豆（Haricots Verts）：约1磅（约450克）    黄油：3汤匙    小葱头（shallot）：1个，剥皮切碎    盐和新鲜磨碎的黑胡椒：适量    新鲜柠檬汁：1茶匙    可选配料：烤杏仁、培根碎、烤大蒜、火腿丁    -- --     将青豆和2杯水放入大煎锅中煮沸，煮至青豆刚变软但仍脆，约5分钟，偶尔翻动。    青豆和水一起沥干，放在一边备用。    在煎锅中加入黄油，用中高火加热直到黄油融化，然后加入切碎的小葱头，炒约1分钟。    将青豆加回锅中，拌匀。根据口味用盐和黑胡椒调味，挤入一些新鲜柠檬汁。-- --     牛肉勃艮第 特级初榨橄榄油 (Extra-virgin olive oil)培根 (Bacon)牛肉 (Beef brisket or chuck steak)大胡萝卜 (Large carrot)白洋葱 (White onion)大蒜 (Garlic)盐和新鲜磨碎的黑胡椒 (Coarse salt and freshly ground pepper)面粉 (Flour)小珍珠洋葱 (Small pearl onions)红酒 (Red wine)牛肉汤 (Beef stock)番茄酱 (Tomato paste)牛肉肉汤块 (Beef bullion cube)新鲜百里香 (Fresh thyme)新鲜欧芹 (Fresh parsley)月桂叶 (Bay leaves)新鲜蘑菇 (Fresh mushrooms)黄油 (Butter)-- -- 在大型炖锅中加热油，炒培根至脆，然后取出备用。牛肉用纸巾吸干，分批在油/培根脂中煎至两面金黄，取出备用。在剩余的油/培根脂中炒胡萝卜和洋葱至软化，加入大蒜炒1分钟。加入牛肉和培根，撒上面粉拌匀，煮4-5分钟。加入小洋葱、红酒、足够覆盖肉的牛肉汤、番茄酱、肉汤块、香料，煮沸。转入烤箱，以175°C烤2-3小时，直到牛肉柔嫩。最后5分钟，用黄油炒蘑菇，加入炖肉中。将炖肉过滤，收集汤汁。将肉和蘑菇放回锅中，倒入汤汁，煮沸至浓稠。

column3: 🔃🏥维A酸0.025%乳膏 (Tretinoin 0.025% Cream) PM [🌈每日清单.md](obsidian://open?vault=BJ's&file=%F0%9F%8C%88%E6%AF%8F%E6%97%A5%E6%B8%85%E5%8D%95.md)
column6: ![image](6604aa6373c6b4000000025f/3def4e919a71c4b8d7458553.png)每晚一次，在洗澡后，睡前使用。用温和的肥皂或清洁剂清洗要处理的皮肤。轻轻拍干。等待20-30分钟，然后涂药。在清洁干燥的皮肤上涂抹一层薄薄的药膏，避免眼睛、嘴唇和鼻子周围的区域。使用后，避免阳光直射，使用FP15防晒霜。*用药前后至少 1 小时内不要淋浴、沐浴或游泳。*避免长时间暴露在风、寒冷或阳光等极端天气下。

column6: 把这种药放在冰箱里。每天早上涂抹轻轻地将药物擦入患处，直至均匀分布。该药可能会漂白织物或头发。避免长时间或过度暴露在阳光下。使用 SPF 15 或更高的防晒霜。![image](6604aa5e73c6b4000000024b/ab7d401da80ea9d4a76d72c7.png)

column6: Scalp / eyebrow / nose 头皮 / 眉毛 / 鼻子![image](3b7548f8acdce6e6216db482/6bcb4db78ff53846fbfecee0.png)涂抹在受影响的皮肤上。在使用前，确保皮肤干燥清洁。涂抹一层薄薄的药膏，轻轻按摩至吸收。避免接触眼睛，不要在破损或受损的皮肤上使用。使用后，如果可能，避免覆盖受影响区域。使用这种药物后洗手，除非您的手是正在治疗的区域的一部分

column6: Scalp / eyebrow / nose 头皮 / 眉毛 / 鼻子![image](65fd282573c6b400000000ab/d8c4405a96410103bb105d3c.png)涂抹在受影响的皮肤上。在使用前，确保皮肤干燥清洁。涂抹一层薄薄的药膏，轻轻按摩至吸收。避免接触眼睛，不要在破损或受损的皮肤上使用。使用后，如果可能，避免覆盖受影响区域。![image](65fd282573c6b400000000ab/d8c4405a96410103bb105d3c.png)使用这种药物后洗手，除非您的手是正在治疗的区域的一部分

column6: ### Step 1: Choose a Company Name- **Action Items**: Visit the California Secretary of State website and use the name search tool to ensure "BJ Studio Digital LLC" is not already taken.- **Materials Needed**: Company name.- **Considerations**: The name must be unique, cannot be similar to any existing company registered in California, and must end with "LLC".- **Interaction With**: California Secretary of State's website name search tool.### Step 2: Choose a Registered Agent- **Action Items**: Select a registered agent. You may use your home address in Palm Springs as the registered address.- **Materials Needed**: Home address information.- **Considerations**: The registered agent must be a California resident or a business that is authorized to act as a registered agent.- **Interaction With**: No third-party interaction required.### Step 3: Prepare and File the Articles of Organization- **Action Items**: Download and fill out the Form LLC-1, including the LLC name, registered agent information, business address, and a description of the business's nature.- **Materials Needed**: LLC name, registered agent information, business address, description of business nature.- **Considerations**: Ensure the form is fully and accurately completed.- **Interaction With**: California Secretary of State's Office.- **Cost**: A $70 state filing fee is required upon submission.### Step 4: Financial and Tax Compliance- **Action Items**:  - Apply for an Employer Identification Number (EIN) on the IRS website.  - Use the EIN to open a business bank account.  - Establish an accounting system to record all business transactions.  - Understand and comply with tax obligations, including self-employment tax and potential state taxes.- **Materials Needed**: Personal information, LLC information, business account information.- **Considerations**: Ensure compliance with all federal, state, and local tax requirements.- **Interaction With**: Internal Revenue Service (IRS), banks, accountants.### Step 5: Business Operations and Compliance- **Action Items**:  - Create an Operating Agreement to clarify the rights and responsibilities among owners.  - Pay the annual $800 California franchise tax.  - Obtain necessary licenses and permits to operate legally.  - Maintain good financial and operational records.  - Regularly review business compliance.- **Materials Needed**: Operating Agreement, business license application form, financial records.- **Considerations**: Ensure business activities are legal and comply with all relevant regulations.- **Interaction With**: Palm Springs City Government, accountants.### Step 6: Obtain Necessary Licenses and Permits- **Action Items**: Based on the nature of the business, confirm the required business license and/or sales permit.- **Materials Needed**: Business description, LLC information, possible additional documents.- **Considerations**: Consider specific industry requirements or restrictions that may apply to your business.- **Interaction With**: Palm Springs City Government, California regulatory agencies for specific industries.### Step 7: Tax Handling- **Action Items**:  - File taxes as a sole proprietor, reporting LLC income and expenses on a Schedule C form.  - Understand the calculation and payment timings for self-employment tax.- **S Corporation Tax Treatment** (Optional):  - File Form 2553 with the IRS to elect S Corporation tax classification.  - Avoid double taxation; income and losses are reported directly on the members' personal income tax returns.  - Pay reasonable salaries to members working in the LLC, and pay Social Security and Medicare taxes on those wages.- **Materials Needed**: Personal income tax return form, Form 2553 (if opting for S Corporation tax treatment).- **Considerations**: Opting for S Corporation tax treatment may require additional tax planning and compliance efforts.- **Interaction With**: Internal Revenue Service (IRS), tax advisors (if opting for S Corporation tax treatment).-

column6: ![image](65d9b0657c3c514535b4d8fc/3def4e919a71c4b8d7458553.png)每晚一次，在洗澡后，睡前使用。用温和的肥皂或清洁剂清洗要处理的皮肤。轻轻拍干。等待20-30分钟，然后涂药。在清洁干燥的皮肤上涂抹一层薄薄的药膏，避免眼睛、嘴唇和鼻子周围的区域。使用后，避免阳光直射，使用FP15防晒霜。*用药前后至少 1 小时内不要淋浴、沐浴或游泳。*避免长时间暴露在风、寒冷或阳光等极端天气下。
